    notes: "AFFC Appendix: 'CERSEI LANNISTER, the First of Her Name, widow of King Robert I Baratheon, Queen Dowager, Protector of the Realm, Lady of Casterly Rock, and Queen Regent.' Cersei became Queen Dowager upon Robert's death in 298 AC."
